{"tid":2342464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白羅斯抗爭｜當局故意讓武漢肺炎監獄內傳播  威脅在囚抗爭者健康","createTime":"2020-12-27T06:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:09:05.000Z","uid":227801,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3883a955fd31cebcb9d01e7a63c04df66e0812d8","tid":2342464,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201227/UUD2WWVNHZCURCTAFFQAR444JQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201227%2FUUD2WWVNHZCURCTAFFQAR444JQ%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=8984f0df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201227%2FUUD2WWVNHZCURCTAFFQAR444JQ%2F&h=54dadf0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201227/UUD2WWVNHZCURCTAFFQAR444JQ/</a><br />\n白羅斯今年爆發反政府示威，當局大舉鎮壓並拘捕大量反政府抗爭者，估計逾3萬人因此被捕。而白羅斯多座監獄更爆發武漢肺炎疫情，有抗爭者在囚禁期間受感染，他們獲釋後投訴監獄十分擁擠、衞生情況惡劣，批評白羅斯當局漠視武漢肺炎病毒，甚至樂見病毒在抗爭者之間傳播。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n利塞茨基憶述，他之前和同伴被關在明斯克監獄時，要4人一起睡在一間2人監房，結果他們4人全部染疫。利塞茨基接受治療出院後，仍要回到監獄服完餘下刑期。他指責白羅斯政府容許武肺病毒在監獄傳播，是出現政治考慮，「守衞公開地說他們是按命令、刻意這樣做」。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"cde41a24003b06985e60d32cf586784c925a032a","tid":2342464,"uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"香港人請參考"},{"pid":"62b9a031c57d20878e9068a591f48e6ea1b87981","tid":2342464,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0ce247bf81b2c99a98fb7ef27d5c40f289d168","tid":2342464,"uid":227801,"like":